reviewText: Shame MGM has included the non-anamorphic version of Jack the Giant Killer in this 3 disc set. Otherwise a cheap and good buy.
I love the movies. It is a must for those who appreciate classic tales.

I purchased this item just to have the Sleeping Beauty film, as all the others have previously been released on DVD.  It is a 2 double-sided disc set.  The theatrical trailers are included as a bonus.  Picture and sound quality are lovely;  Sleeping Beauty is a widescreen presentation.  All others are exactly the same as their previous DVD releases.
